sentences: Leather Leone is an American metal vocalist and lyricist, best known for fronting the groups Rude Girl and Chastain in the 1980s.
She released one solo album, Shock Waves, in 1989, before taking a twenty-year break from the music scene.
In 2011 she began performing again in The Sledge/Leather Project, which released a debut heavy metal album, Imagine Me Alive, in 2012.

Leather Leone started singing in the early 1980s.
Leather Leone guest sang on a released highly collectible "Rude Girls" 2-song 12" EP in 1987.
The group was put together in 1984 by Mike Varney, president of Shrapnel Records for a David T. Chastain solo album.
She recorded five albums with him over six years, and the group at different points contained members from Alice Cooper, Cannibal Corpse, and King Diamond.
